title: Oingo Boingo Rarities
description: I downloaded this from another site using tpb trackers, but it didn&#039;t appear to be available here. I absolutely love all things Elfman/Boingo, and there&#039;s some completely wonderful stuff here. I particularly love Open Eyes, Kiss My Ass, Water (very strange version of a song I had only heard on Farewell previously), and Commando Girls. Quality varies, some of these are very crappy recordings, but musically I just love these guys. I&#039;m proud to make it available on TPB. If anybody knows where to get the video for Farewell, I&#039;d greatly appreciate it. I found a copy of the DVD on amazon for over $100 wtf!?!?!? The VHS I found for 10 bucks...that didn&#039;t make much sense to me. I used to have the VHS, but it was lost years ago, I&#039;d love to get it again. I appreciate any help you might have for me on that one, hope you enjoy this release, it&#039;s Boingo-licious!
